大家好，我是神秘高手k

模型介绍：

DPM++ 2M Karras  20-30步即可。

The 2D flat color block style is very suitable for copying and practicing marker coloring, with almost no gradient areas.

Présentation du modèle:

Style de bloc de couleur plat 2D, idéal pour la pratique de la copie sur le marqueur de couleur, presque aucune zone de dégradé.

Mots indicateurs négatifs recommandés:

(malformed hands, malformed fingers, malformed legs:1.4), (poorly drawn hands, poorly drawn face), (text, signature, watermark, username),nsfw,(EasyNegative), (bad-hands-5), verybadimagenegative_v1.3, (worst quality, low quality:1.2), (missing fingers, missing hands, missing legs:1.4) (extra limbs, extra fingers, extra hands, extra legs:1.4), (mutate fingers, mutated hands, mutated legs:1.4),

Méthode d'échantillonnage:

DPM + + 2m Karras 20 - 30 étapes suffisent.

Algorithme de grossissement: R-ESRGAN 4x+Anime6B

 Представление модели: 

 Стиль 2D плоских цветовых блоков идеально подходит для практики копирования окраски ручки Марка, почти без градиентов в области.

 Метод отбора проб: 

 DPM + + 2M Karras 20 - 30 шагов.

Introducción al modelo:

El estilo de bloque de color plano 2d es muy adecuado para copiar y practicar el coloreado del marcador, con pocas áreas degradadas.

Consejos negativos recomendados:

items.name: Change-A-Character: Evil Sailor Scout, Your Waifu Has Joined the Force of Evil!
items.description:
What does it do you ask?

Fighting evil by moonlight, Winning love by daylight... "Nah, that sounds boring," thinks your waifu as Sailor Moon is victorious yet again. In fact, wouldn't it be more fun if the bad guys win for once? So, with her choice being made, she decides to join the forces of evil and just cause a teensy bitsy amount of mayham.

How to use it:

(I use Sampling Method DPM++ SDE Karras and Upscaler R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B).

0.6 to 1 depending on model/lora/etc combination.

Main Trigger

EvlSM - Base tag to get the transformation

sailor senshi uniform - The classic-ish Sailor Scout look. Feel free to remove if you want your own outfit.

long legs, crescent, crescent facial mark, makeup, lipstick, mascara, eyeshadow - How I like the evil sailor scout to look... But you can also adjust.

Other Useful Tags

half updo, very long hair, twin tails, double bun, hair bun, cone hair bun,  long legs, sailor venus, thighhighs, sailor senshi uniform, sailor_collar, skirt, bare legs, choker, fishnets, orange_skirt, orange_sailor_collar, red_bow, gloves, high_heels, fishnet_thighhighs, hair_bow, orange_choker, shoes, jewelry, magical_girl, elbow_gloves, tiara, adapted_costume, garter_straps, strappy_heels, earrings, makeup, lipstick, brooch, black_thighhighs, shorts, short shorts, swimsuit, bikini, turtleneck, hat, dress,  star earrings, sailor shirt, sleeveless, pumps, crescent earrings, eyeshadow, mascara, bodysuit, crescent, crescent facial mark, facial mark, forehead mark, sailor shirt, pleated skirt - Common tags in the dataset.

Whatever else you want!

Extra, Extra!: Should be well trained and usable in most models. Images shown for example.

Picture Descriptions:

1: MistoonAnime with just this Lora.

2-4: Hasaku with just this Lora.

5-6: RevAnimated with just this Lora.

7: DreamShaper with just this Lora.

8: Hasaku combo'd with my in progress in progress Ninja Locon.

9: Hasaku combo'd with my released Masked Evil Locon.

10: Hasaku combo'd with my released Ada Lora.

11: Hasaku combo'd with my released Evelynn Lora.

12: Hasaku combo'd with my released Lucoa Lora.

How was it trained?

It was trained on animefull_final with 40 images with the usual self-pruning and tagging and a wide range of different images. I like keeping my prompts simple for the first few pictures so that you can see it without a whole bunch of mumbo jumbo. Make your pictures better than mine though!

What's next for this?

Should be good!

What's next that isn't this?

More character Loras. (Freya from Danmachi, Mio and Ushio from Summertime Render, Miu and Junko and Kaede and Maki from Danganronpa, Akane Shinjo from SSSS. And maybe Wilhelm van Astrea, my favorite Re:Zero husbando or a Prinny from Disgaea.

READ!

This is my first lora, the goal was to get more interesting lighting and contrast in images.

Yes, this will have a strong impact on images, it will change the contrast, colors and subject at higher strengths. I will leave tips on how to use it below, but please experiment with it further than me. I have attached some sample images made with the lora and some xyz plots to see the lora’s effect. 

HIRESFIX is HIGHLY recommended!

TIPS ON HOW TO USE IT

If you are fine with it changing the image, then you can simply use it as any other lora. recommended weights from my testing and personal use, 0.4 - 0.8, this all depends on what you want it to do and if you are using it combined with other lora’s. 

Another thing that I have been doing when I feel like the lora is holding back the flexibility, do  THIS. When using it, use it at lower weight in the prompt, 0.2 - 0.4. Then when you find an image you like, use hires fix or img2img, now you can use the lora at a higher strength in the hires fix prompt. I like doing 0.4 in the normal prompt and 0.8 or higher in the hires fix prompt. This allows you to layer more lora’s and less changes with the subject of the image.

ALSO! I recommend trying different types of lighting, like “Green lighting, green tint” etc… I usually combine this with BREAK at the start of the color. 

Lora was made for realism but works great with stylized.

items.description:
大家好，我是chosen鲷，这次给大家带来的是素描感lora。

啥叫素描感呢？这个稍微有点不太好解释，指的就是一种上色技法，也就是AO画法，即在上色之前，先用灰阶图把画面元素的亮部暗部全部画好，等于先把整体的素描关系确定了，然后再上颜色，一般一个区域之上一种颜色。（解释起来稍微有点抽象，如果你画过画的话你应该能明白我在说啥）

这种风格的图的特点就是人物会显得很立体，然后颜色只是灰度在变，暗部会很暗已经接近于死黑了，色相是不会变的，属于是藤原 mika那种疯狂变色相的画法的反面了，因为这种风格被广泛应用于明日方舟游戏立绘中，所以我也打上了arknights的tag，很适合出舟游人物，也很适合画涩图，建议当做一种画风lora使用.

推荐的tag：

, (masterpiece:1.2), best quality,PIXIV,

这里描述你要画的内容，抽卡的话他更倾向于出俯视图

<lora:sketch style_20230721202436:0.8>

Negative prompt: EasyNegative, badhandsv5-neg,Subtitles,word,
Steps: 32, Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras, CFG scale: 7, Seed: 1953073089, Size: 512x768, Model hash: 0ac9feaf4e, Model: chosen impasto-mix, Denoising strength: 0.5, Clip skip: 2, Hires upscale: 2, Hires upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+, Lora hashes: "sketch style_20230721202436: 4414811dc280", Version: v1.4.1

Hi, I'm chosen 鲷, and this time I'm bringing you the AO style lora.

What is sketch sense? This is a little bit not very good to explain, refers to a coloring technique, that is, AO painting, that is, before coloring, first use the gray scale map to draw all the bright and dark parts of the screen elements, which is equal to determining the overall sketch relationship first, and then on the color, generally a color above an area. (It's a little abstract, but if you've ever painted, you know what I'm talking about.)

The characteristic of this style of drawing is that the characters will appear very three-dimensional, and then the color is only changing in gray level, the dark part will be very dark and close to dead black, and the hue will not change, which belongs to the opposite of Fujiwara mika's crazy color-changing phase painting, because this style is widely used in the game of Ark of Tomorrow. Therefore, I also put on the arknights tag, which is very suitable for sailing characters, and it is also very suitable for drawing astringent pictures, and it is recommended to use lora as a painting style.

items.name: Gloomifier slider LECO
items.description:
Gloomifier currently has 3 versions. Please read blow for information about each one of them!

Gloomifiers are simple LECO's that makes images gloomier on positive and happier on negative. Can go from really low weights to really high weights giving different results.

Gloomifier The Dread

Negative weight gives really happy results. Can go down to -1.5 weight or even further. Depends on model how it reacts

Positive weight makes the image darker and dreadier. Weight can go to +3 giving stronger results. Depends on model how it reacts.

Does not require trigger words, but helping words that makes images darker, creepier can help. For example dread, dark lighting,glowing eyes etc...

Gloomifier The glow

Weights -3 to 5 give decent results

Can go even lower or higher giving stronger results. Results may wary between models. Meina V11 gave good results.

Does not require trigger word, but helping words like: bioluminescence, dark, night,darkness, cold, cold lighting, fog, glowing, can give stronger and different results.

Gloomifier The Darkifier

Positive makes the images darker and negative makes images more light

Please leave some images, i'd love to see them (～￣▽￣)～

This is a LoHa, which means you need this extension.

This model is intended to generate female-on-female sex scenes with the use of a strap-on. It is still experimental as it is capable of creating these scenes but may generate extra limbs or bad scenes, as this LoHa generally requires multiple generations and tweaking to get what you want or use of img2img/inpainting.

I have separated the dataset into three general positions, receiving from behind (ass fuck ), straddling position (straddling fuck ), and lying position. (lying fuck ). I suggest you include one of these three tags, as well as the base tag strap-on sex. Generally, you should weight it between 0.8-1, decreasing the weight may make it more flexible but also will decrease correct placement and color of dildo.

Each position has different tags you can use to improve quality, and I suggest looking at examples as well as playing with the prompts to increase generation quality. For example, if you have issues with only 1 woman generating, adding 2girls can help. Or for the straddling position, often only 1 face may be visible. Adding face out of frame to the negative can help reduce this issue.

items.description:
Hinata Aki from Keroro Gunsou / ケロロ軍曹

This is my first release of a LoRA model to the public. Your feedback is valuable, so please feel free to rate the model or share your creations with it. I'd be thrilled to see its applications. If you find it useful, consider showing your appreciation by buying me a coffee.

  • Weight: between 0.8 to 1.0

  • Trigger Word: hinata_aki

  • Additional Prompts: mature female, glasses, rimless eyewear, round eyewear, blue eyes, blue hair

Suggested Hires.fix configuration:

  • Upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B

  • Hires steps: between 10 to 20

  • Denoising strength: between 0.15 to 0.25

One of my favourite tasks is transitioning characters from anime to photorealistic renditions or vice versa. The results are always unpredictable, and the anticipation until the final render is exhilarating. This LoRA model performs well in photorealistic settings, and yes, it can be used for NSFW content too.

Your comments or suggestions are not only welcome but can significantly improve the quality of my models. They also motivate me to create more LoRA models. Feel free to connect with me on my Discord channel.

For those intrigued about the training process, V3 was trained on the AnyLoRA base model with a dataset comprised of 59 images.

The compatibility of this LoRA model has been tested and work well with the following base models:

Anime models:

  • MeinaMix V11

  • Cetus-Mix (WhaleFall2)

  • Babes V2

Photorealistic models:

  • AbsoluteReality V1

  • CosplayMix V4.2

All demonstration images showcased are randomly selected, not handpicked for optimal results.

items.name: Pathfinder
items.description:
💚 for Updates - I would love to see your reviews and images of this model, feel free to post them below!

Pathfinder branches from Maverick's flexibility fusing in Nu Element and other resources to further expand on expressive fantasy elements along with a stronger cartoon/animation styling. This model offers a wide range of creativity from flat 2D styles, anime/illustration, cartoon/animation, semi-realistic styles + more. I would love to see the styles you come up with!

💡 This model is currently somewhat of an experimental project.

Recommended Use

There is a lot of variation in parameters for what works. Be aware on the styling you're choosing and use what you find best. The example images, gallery sections, and the quick start below are good starting points.

~20 steps, 7 scale, ~0.3-0.5 denoising, clip skip 1 or 2

Disclaimer

This model(s) may output NSFW content unintentionally depending on parameters used. Make sure you tailor your prompts accordingly. For example "nsfw" in the negative prompt.

The purpose of sharing this model is not to showcase obscene material in a public forum. The use of this learning model is entirely at the discretion of the user, and they have the freedom to choose whether or not to create SFW or NSFW content. The decision of whether to engage with SFW or NSFW content lies with the user and their own personal preferences. The ai model(s) do not contain explicit visual content that can be accessed easily.

Example Images used

  • vae-ft-ema-560000-ema vae

  • 4x-UltraSharp or R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B upscalers

  • hires fix w/ some upscaled again using SD upscale

  • use old karras scheduler signmas (0.1 to 10) compatibility setting

  • any LoRa use should be listed in the image metadata

  • Bad_v2 negative embedding renamed should be the same as bad_prompt_version2

  • EasyNegative and badhandv4 negative embeddings were also used

*Negative embeddings are optional
